    },
    "content": {
      "html": "<p>I believe I am expected to tell you all about geometry; what it is, its developments through the centuries, its current issues and problems, and, if possible, a peep into the future.</p>"
    },
    "tags": [
      "differential geometry",
      "manifolds",
      "topology"
    ],
