    "date": "1979-05-01",
    "source": {
      "work": "From Triangles to Manifolds",
      "chapter": null
    },
    "content": {
      "html": "<p>The linking number L is determined by the formula \\(T + W = L\\).</p>"
    },
    "tags": [
